    :root {
      --pink: #F84CA2;
      --dark-blue: #1c2663;
      --white: #FFFFFF;
      --text-black: #404040;
      --text-gray: #737373;
      --text-placeholder: rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.3);
      --back-white: #FAFAFA;
      --back-gray: #EDF1F4;
      --back-blue: #091355;
      --back-light-pink: #ffd8e8;
      --back-light-blue: #6fc2ff;
      --warm-milk: #fff9f3;
      --warm-apricot: #ffe4d2;
      --warm-butter: #fff0b8;
      --warm-coral: #ff9f7e;
      --warm-mint: #e7fbf4;
      --shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.11);
      --ruled-line: #F2F2F2;
      --gradient-primary: linear-gradient(90deg, #1ddcff, #4db4ff);
      --gradient-pink: linear-gradient(90deg, #f84ca2, #f84ca2);
      --gradient-sunrise: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff9f3 0%, #ffe7ef 48%, #edf8ff 100%);
      --gradient-card: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.98), rgba(255,255,255,0.94));
      --gradient-night: linear-gradient(180deg, #091355 0%, #1d2e93 100%);
      --font-sans: "Noto Sans JP", "Hiragino Sans", "Yu Gothic", sans-serif;
      --font-note: "Hiragino Maru Gothic ProN", "Segoe Print", "Comic Sans MS", cursive;
      --radius-sm: 5px;
      --radius-md: 12px;
      --radius-card: 13px;
      --radius-lg: 16px;
      --radius-chip: 22px;
      --radius-button: 30px;
      --radius-phone: 36px;
      --shadow-light: 0 10px 28px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.10);
      --shadow-medium: 0 18px 48px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.15);
      --shadow-heavy: 0 28px 72px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.22);
      --phone-width: 375px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100%;
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      color: var(--text-black);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 10% 10%, rgba(255, 203, 170, 0.26), transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 8%, rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.18), transparent 22%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 90% 88%, rgba(111, 194, 255, 0.18), transparent 24%),
        #fffaf7;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before,
    body::after {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      width: 280px;
      height: 280px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      filter: blur(46px);
      opacity: 0.48;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    body::before {
      top: 32px;
      left: -92px;
      background: rgba(255, 176, 128, 0.26);
    }

    body::after {
      right: -96px;
      bottom: 8px;
      background: rgba(77, 180, 255, 0.20);
    }

    button {
      font: inherit;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1380px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 18px 14px 52px;
    }

    .masthead {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 20px 18px 22px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }

    .masthead::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: 240px;
      height: 240px;
      right: -36px;
      bottom: -72px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.18), transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      min-height: 36px;
      padding: 0 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .eyebrow .pulse {
      width: 9px;
      height: 9px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--pink);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.12);
      animation: pulse 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 16px 0 10px;
      max-width: 880px;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: clamp(32px, 5.8vw, 56px);
      line-height: 1.16;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .lead {
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0;
      color: #68728d;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.9;
    }

    .lead strong {
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .lead .marker {
      background: linear-gradient(transparent 60%, rgba(255, 232, 132, 0.86) 60%);
      padding: 0 2px;
    }

    .kpi-strip {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .kpi-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      min-height: 38px;
      padding: 0 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .kpi-pill strong {
      color: var(--pink);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .kpi-pill.soft {
      background: rgba(255, 245, 223, 0.94);
    }

    .control-panel {
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 26px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.80);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .control-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .control-label {
      min-width: 112px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .chip-button,
    .mode-button,
    .focus-button,
    .compare-switch {
      appearance: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      min-height: 43px;
      padding: 0 16px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-button);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 180ms ease, background 180ms ease, color 180ms ease, border-color 180ms ease;
    }

    .chip-button:hover,
    .mode-button:hover,
    .focus-button:hover,
    .compare-switch:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .chip-button.is-active,
    .mode-button.is-active,
    .focus-button.is-active,
    .compare-switch.is-active {
      background: var(--gradient-pink);
      color: var(--white);
      border-color: rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.22);
    }

    .deck {
      display: grid;
      gap: 24px;
      margin-top: 22px;
    }

    .shot {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      transition: transform 220ms ease, box-shadow 220ms ease, opacity 220ms ease;
    }

    .shot.is-focused {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-heavy);
    }

    .shot-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .shot-tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      min-height: 32px;
      padding: 0 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #fff4f8;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .shot-tag.android {
      background: #eff8ff;
    }

    .shot-tag.compare {
      background: #fff7e9;
    }

    .shot-title {
      margin: 6px 0 0;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .shot-desc {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      max-width: 600px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .shot-note {
      max-width: 220px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .shot-note strong {
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .phone {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: var(--phone-width);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-phone);
      background: #20253f;
      box-shadow: 0 26px 56px rgba(9, 19, 85, 0.30);
    }

    .phone::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 8px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 128px;
      height: 26px;
      border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px;
      background: #11152a;
      z-index: 5;
    }

    .phone.android::before {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      top: 10px;
    }

    .screen {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 760px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--gradient-sunrise);
    }

    .screen::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(circle at 18% 14%, rgba(255,255,255,0.78), transparent 18%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 82% 12%, rgba(255,255,255,0.62), transparent 16%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .screen.ai {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 84% 12%, rgba(255,255,255,0.86), transparent 18%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #fff8f2 0%, #ffe7ef 46%, #ecf8ff 100%);
    }

    .screen.life {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 86% 16%, rgba(255,255,255,0.82), transparent 16%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #fff7ef 0%, #fff0dd 24%, #eef8ff 100%);
    }

    .screen.compare {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 14% 10%, rgba(255,255,255,0.80), transparent 18%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #fffaf3 0%, #ffe8ef 50%, #eef7ff 100%);
    }

    .status-bar {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 12px 18px 8px;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      padding: 8px 18px 0;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 126px;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero h2,
    .compare-top h2 {
      margin: 8px 0;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 33px;
      line-height: 1.26;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .hero p,
    .compare-top p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #666b88;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .line-mark {
      display: inline;
      background: linear-gradient(transparent 60%, rgba(255, 224, 116, 0.8) 60%);
      padding: 0 2px;
    }

    .badge-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .mini-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      min-height: 32px;
      padding: 0 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .mini-badge.pink {
      background: rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.14);
      color: #ba246e;
    }

    .mini-badge.yellow {
      background: rgba(255, 239, 182, 0.88);
    }

    .mini-badge.blue {
      background: rgba(109, 194, 255, 0.16);
    }

    .doodle,
    .doodle-life {
      position: relative;
      width: 124px;
      height: 134px;
      margin-left: auto;
    }

    .blob {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 12px 10px 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fffefa 0%, #fff0f6 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.12);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .car {
      position: absolute;
      left: 18px;
      bottom: 20px;
      width: 86px;
      height: 38px;
      border-radius: 22px 24px 14px 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ff98ba 0%, #f84ca2 100%);
    }

    .car::before,
    .car::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -8px;
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--dark-blue);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 4px #fff;
    }

    .car::before {
      left: 12px;
    }

    .car::after {
      right: 12px;
    }

    .face {
      position: absolute;
      right: 12px;
      top: 18px;
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #fff7d8;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .face::before,
    .face::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 18px;
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .face::before {
      left: 14px;
    }

    .face::after {
      right: 14px;
    }

    .smile {
      position: absolute;
      left: 15px;
      bottom: 12px;
      width: 18px;
      height: 9px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid var(--dark-blue);
      border-radius: 0 0 18px 18px;
    }

    .wallet {
      position: absolute;
      left: 22px;
      bottom: 18px;
      width: 84px;
      height: 58px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #7fd1ff 0%, #4db4ff 100%);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .wallet::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 8px;
      right: 8px;
      top: 16px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    }

    .coin {
      position: absolute;
      right: 12px;
      top: 24px;
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #fff3b5;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: #c67b00;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .sticky {
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 3;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-family: var(--font-note);
      animation: floatNote 5.6s ease-in-out infinite;
      transform-origin: center;
    }

    .note-a1 {
      top: 126px;
      left: 18px;
      background: #fff4bf;
      transform: rotate(-7deg);
    }

    .note-a2 {
      top: 176px;
      right: 18px;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #ff7d63;
      transform: rotate(6deg);
      animation-delay: 1.1s;
    }

    .note-b1 {
      top: 132px;
      right: 18px;
      background: #fff8d9;
      transform: rotate(-6deg);
    }

    .note-b2 {
      top: 186px;
      left: 18px;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #3c73af;
      transform: rotate(6deg);
      animation-delay: 1.3s;
    }

    .note-c1 {
      top: 124px;
      left: 18px;
      background: #fff4bf;
      transform: rotate(-6deg);
    }

    .note-c2 {
      top: 174px;
      right: 20px;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #ff7d63;
      transform: rotate(5deg);
      animation-delay: 1.4s;
    }

    .card {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      margin: 16px 16px 0;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-card);
      background: var(--gradient-card);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .card.dark {
      background: var(--gradient-night);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .card-head,
    .expense-total {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .card-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .card-caption {
      margin: 4px 0 0;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .card.dark .card-caption {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
    }

    .price {
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 38px;
      line-height: 1.08;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .yen {
      margin-left: 4px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .pill-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      min-height: 30px;
      padding: 0 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #f3f8ff;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .card.dark .pill {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .graph,
    .mini-graph {
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 12px 12px 10px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background:
        repeating-linear-gradient(to top, rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.06) 0 1px, transparent 1px 24px),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff, #fbfdff);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .graph svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 120px;
      display: block;
    }

    .mini-graph svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 94px;
      display: block;
    }

    .graph-area {
      fill: rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.12);
    }

    .graph-line {
      fill: none;
      stroke: var(--pink);
      stroke-width: 4;
      stroke-linecap: round;
      stroke-linejoin: round;
      stroke-dasharray: 320;
      stroke-dashoffset: 320;
      animation: drawLine 1.6s ease forwards;
    }

    .graph-line.blue {
      stroke: #4db4ff;
    }

    .graph-dot {
      fill: var(--pink);
      stroke: #fff;
      stroke-width: 3;
      animation: pulseDot 2.6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .graph-dot.blue {
      fill: #4db4ff;
    }

    .graph-labels {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-top: 8px;
      color: #7b7f97;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .three-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .mini-stat,
    .forecast-box {
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.05);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .mini-stat strong,
    .forecast-box strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.35;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .mini-stat span,
    .forecast-box span {
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .primary-button,
    .secondary-button,
    .ghost-button {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 43px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: var(--radius-button);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 180ms ease, filter 180ms ease;
    }

    .primary-button {
      margin-top: 14px;
      background: var(--gradient-primary);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .secondary-button {
      margin-top: 10px;
      background: var(--gradient-pink);
      color: var(--white);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .ghost-button {
      margin-top: 10px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .primary-button:hover,
    .secondary-button:hover,
    .ghost-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      filter: saturate(1.03);
    }

    .expense-amount {
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 34px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .expense-meta {
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .expense-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    .expense-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .expense-dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }

    .expense-bar {
      position: relative;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #eef3f8;
    }

    .expense-fill {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0 auto 0 0;
      width: 50%;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.85), rgba(77, 180, 255, 0.85));
      transition: width 280ms ease;
    }

    .forecast-card {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .memory-strip {
      margin: 16px 16px 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .memory-card {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .memory-icon {
      flex: 0 0 34px;
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: #fff0c7;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .memory-text strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .memory-text span {
      display: block;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .compare-hero {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      padding: 14px 18px 0;
    }

    .compare-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .compare-badge {
      min-width: 112px;
      min-height: 58px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .compare-badge strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--pink);
      font-size: 28px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .compare-badge span {
      display: block;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .compare-toggle {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      margin: 14px 18px 0;
      padding: 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .compare-switch {
      flex: 1;
      min-height: 39px;
      box-shadow: none;
      background: transparent;
      border: 0;
      padding: 0 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .compare-table {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      margin: 16px 16px 0;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .compare-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .compare-head,
    .compare-cell {
      padding: 12px 8px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .compare-head {
      background: #f6f9ff;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .compare-head.ucarpac {
      background: rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.12);
    }

    .compare-cell {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 82px;
      background: #fffdfa;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .compare-cell strong {
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .compare-cell.ucarpac {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.12), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96));
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.12);
    }

    .compare-quote {
      margin: 12px 16px 0;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(255, 248, 219, 0.94);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-family: var(--font-note);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .screen-footer {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      margin: 14px 18px 0;
      padding: 10px 0 18px;
      color: #7a819c;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .bottom-notes {
      margin-top: 24px;
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 26px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.80);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .bottom-notes h3 {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .notes-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .note-card {
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .note-card strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .note-card span {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 4px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .toast {
      position: fixed;
      left: 50%;
      bottom: 18px;
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(18px);
      min-width: 240px;
      max-width: calc(100vw - 32px);
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(9, 19, 85, 0.92);
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-heavy);
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity 220ms ease, transform 220ms ease;
      z-index: 50;
    }

    .toast.is-visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.08); }
    }

    @keyframes floatNote {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(var(--r, 0deg)); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-6px) rotate(var(--r, 0deg)); }
    }

    @keyframes drawLine {
      to { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
    }

    @keyframes pulseDot {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.15); }
    }

    @media (min-width: 860px) {
      .deck {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        align-items: start;
      }

      .notes-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 859px) {
      .control-label {
        min-width: auto;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .hero-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 110px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 430px) {
      .page {
        padding: 14px 10px 42px;
      }

      .masthead,
      .control-panel,
      .shot,
      .bottom-notes {
        border-radius: 22px;
      }

      .shot {
        padding: 14px;
      }

      .hero h2,
      .compare-top h2 {
        font-size: 29px;
      }

      .price {
        font-size: 34px;
      }

      .expense-amount {
        font-size: 28px;
      }

      .compare-grid {
        gap: 6px;
      }

      .compare-head,
      .compare-cell {
        padding: 10px 6px;
      }

      .compare-cell strong {
        font-size: 18px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <header class="masthead">
      <div class="eyebrow">
        <span class="pulse"></span>
        ASO検証 2026.04.08 / ストアPV→DL率 改善案
      </div>
      <h1>安心して試せる理由を先に見せて、<br>ダウンロードの迷いをやわらかくほどく。</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        ストア詳細で迷う人が知りたいのは、機能一覧よりも<strong>「このアプリなら怖くなさそう」</strong>という感覚です。
        今回は、<span class="marker">AI査定の安心感</span>、<span class="marker">出費管理と将来予測の納得感</span>、<span class="marker">まずは電話0本で見始められる気軽さ</span>を、
        暖かい色とやさしい言葉でスクリーンショット化しています。
      </p>
      <div class="kpi-strip">
        <div class="kpi-pill"><strong>現状</strong> ストアPV→DL率 17.3%</div>
        <div class="kpi-pill soft"><strong>目標</strong> ストアPV→DL率 25%</div>
        <div class="kpi-pill">軸 AI査定 / 出費管理 / 電話0本</div>
        <div class="kpi-pill">前提 相場チェックは個人情報なし</div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="control-panel">
      <div class="control-row">
        <div class="control-label">注目するスクショ</div>
        <button class="focus-button is-active" type="button" data-focus="a" aria-pressed="true">A / AI査定</button>
        <button class="focus-button" type="button" data-focus="b" aria-pressed="false">B / 出費管理</button>
        <button class="focus-button" type="button" data-focus="c" aria-pressed="false">C / 電話0本</button>
      </div>
      <div class="control-row">
        <div class="control-label">車種を切替</div>
        <button class="chip-button is-active" type="button" data-vehicle="prius" aria-pressed="true">プリウス</button>
        <button class="chip-button" type="button" data-vehicle="serena" aria-pressed="false">セレナ</button>
        <button class="chip-button" type="button" data-vehicle="nbox" aria-pressed="false">N-BOX</button>
      </div>
      <div class="control-row">
        <div class="control-label">利用シーン</div>
        <button class="mode-button is-active" type="button" data-mode="check" aria-pressed="true">まずは相場を見る</button>
        <button class="mode-button" type="button" data-mode="sell" aria-pressed="false">売る相談まで進む</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="deck">
      <article class="shot is-focused" data-shot="a">
        <div class="shot-head">
          <div>
            <div class="shot-tag">iOS向け / スクショA</div>
            <h2 class="shot-title">AI査定を主役にして、<br>「まず入れてみよう」を作る。</h2>
            <p class="shot-desc">
              1枚目は、愛車の価値が見える安心感をまっすぐ伝える構成です。
              数字を見せつつも、圧ではなく「まず知るだけでいい」という温度感を優先しています。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="shot-note">
            <strong>狙い</strong><br />
            価格を見たい比較検討層に対して、最初の一瞬で
            「個人情報なしで試せる」を印象づけます。
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phone">
          <div class="screen ai">
            <div class="status-bar">
              <span>9:41</span>
              <span>UcarPAC</span>
              <span>100%</span>
            </div>

            <div class="sticky note-a1" style="--r:-7deg;">あとで売るでも<br />だいじょうぶ。</div>
            <div class="sticky note-a2" style="--r:6deg;">相場チェックは<br />電話0本</div>

            <section class="hero">
              <div class="hero-grid">
                <div>
                  <h2 id="a-hook">AIがあなたの愛車を査定</h2>
                  <p id="a-support">
                    相場が見えると、気持ちは少し軽くなる。
                    <span class="line-mark">まだ売らなくても</span>、まずは今日の価値を知るところから。
                  </p>
                  <div class="badge-row">
                    <div class="mini-badge pink" id="a-badge1">個人情報なしで開始</div>
                    <div class="mini-badge yellow" id="a-badge2">将来予測つき</div>
                    <div class="mini-badge blue" id="a-badge3">8,000社の相場学習</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="doodle" aria-hidden="true">
                  <div class="blob"></div>
                  <div class="face"><div class="smile"></div></div>
                  <div class="car"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section class="card">
              <div class="card-head">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="card-title" id="a-car-name">トヨタ プリウス Z</h3>
                  <p class="card-caption" id="a-car-meta">2021年式 / 28,400km / ブラック</p>
                </div>
                <div class="price" id="a-price">218.6<span class="yen">万円</span></div>
              </div>
              <div class="pill-row">
                <div class="pill" id="a-pill-main">今日のAI査定</div>
                <div class="pill" id="a-pill-range">下限 210.4万円</div>
                <div class="pill" id="a-pill-confidence">信頼度 87%</div>
              </div>
              <div class="graph">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 320 120" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path id="a-area" class="graph-area" d=""></path>
                  <path id="a-line" class="graph-line" d=""></path>
                  <circle id="a-dot-1" class="graph-dot" cx="0" cy="0" r="6"></circle>
                  <circle id="a-dot-2" class="graph-dot" cx="0" cy="0" r="6"></circle>
                  <circle id="a-dot-3" class="graph-dot" cx="0" cy="0" r="6"></circle>
                </svg>
                <div class="graph-labels">
                  <span>今月</span>
                  <span>3ヶ月後</span>
                  <span>6ヶ月後</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="three-grid">
                <div class="mini-stat">
                  <strong id="a-stat-1">+2.4万円</strong>
                  <span>需要の追い風</span>
                </div>
                <div class="mini-stat">
                  <strong id="a-stat-2">6分</strong>
                  <span>入力目安</span>
                </div>
                <div class="mini-stat">
                  <strong id="a-stat-3">0件</strong>
                  <span>営業電話</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <button class="primary-button" type="button" data-toast="写真からAI査定を開始する導線を想定しています。">写真でAI査定をはじめる</button>
              <button class="ghost-button" type="button" data-toast="あとで売る前提でも価値を保存できる導線です。">相場だけ保存する</button>
            </section>

            <div class="screen-footer">
              App Store 1枚目向け想定 / AI査定・個人情報なし・将来予測を一画面で理解
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="shot" data-shot="b">
        <div class="shot-head">
          <div>
            <div class="shot-tag android">Android向け / スクショB</div>
            <h2 class="shot-title">出費管理と将来予測で、<br />“いま売る理由”までやさしく見せる。</h2>
            <p class="shot-desc">
              2枚目は、「見るだけアプリ」で終わらせないための納得感づくりです。
              維持費と価値の両方を見せることで、今すぐ売らない層にも残る理由を作ります。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="shot-note">
            <strong>狙い</strong><br />
            Androidの比較検討層に対して、
            生活管理アプリのような継続価値を伝えます。
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phone android">
          <div class="screen life">
            <div class="status-bar">
              <span>9:41</span>
              <span>Garage</span>
              <span>88%</span>
            </div>

            <div class="sticky note-b1" style="--r:-6deg;">売り時が<br />見えてくる</div>
            <div class="sticky note-b2" style="--r:6deg;">毎月の出費も<br />まとめて見える</div>

            <section class="hero">
              <div class="hero-grid">
                <div>
                  <h2 id="b-hook">出費も、売り時も、<br />ひと目でわかる。</h2>
                  <p id="b-support">
                    車の価値だけでなく、毎月の維持費まで見えると、
                    <span class="line-mark">次の判断がしやすくなる</span>。
                  </p>
                  <div class="badge-row">
                    <div class="mini-badge pink">出費管理つき</div>
                    <div class="mini-badge yellow">6ヶ月予測</div>
                    <div class="mini-badge blue">売り時通知</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="doodle-life" aria-hidden="true">
                  <div class="blob"></div>
                  <div class="coin">¥</div>
                  <div class="wallet"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section class="card">
              <div class="expense-total">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="card-title">今月のクルマ出費</h3>
                  <p class="card-caption" id="b-expense-caption">プリウス / 2026年4月の集計</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="expense-amount" id="b-expense-total">42,800円</div>
                  <div class="expense-meta" id="b-expense-meta">先月より 3,200円ダウン<br />家計負担 7.6%</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="expense-list">
                <div class="expense-item">
                  <span class="expense-dot" style="background:#f84ca2;"></span>
                  <span id="b-label-fuel">ガソリン</span>
                  <span id="b-value-fuel">15,800円</span>
                  <div class="expense-bar" style="grid-column:2 / 4;">
                    <div class="expense-fill" id="b-bar-fuel"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="expense-item">
                  <span class="expense-dot" style="background:#4db4ff;"></span>
                  <span id="b-label-insurance">保険</span>
                  <span id="b-value-insurance">9,700円</span>
                  <div class="expense-bar" style="grid-column:2 / 4;">
                    <div class="expense-fill" id="b-bar-insurance"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="expense-item">
                  <span class="expense-dot" style="background:#ffbe5b;"></span>
                  <span id="b-label-parking">駐車場</span>
                  <span id="b-value-parking">12,000円</span>
                  <div class="expense-bar" style="grid-column:2 / 4;">
                    <div class="expense-fill" id="b-bar-parking"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="expense-item">
                  <span class="expense-dot" style="background:#31c48d;"></span>
                  <span id="b-label-maintenance">整備</span>
                  <span id="b-value-maintenance">5,300円</span>
                  <div class="expense-bar" style="grid-column:2 / 4;">
                    <div class="expense-fill" id="b-bar-maintenance"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="forecast-card">
                <div class="forecast-box">
                  <strong id="b-current-price">218.6万円</strong>
                  <span>いま売る予測価格</span>
                </div>
                <div class="forecast-box">
                  <strong id="b-future-price">207.1万円</strong>
                  <span>6ヶ月後の予測価格</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mini-graph">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 320 94" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path id="b-line" class="graph-line blue" d=""></path>
                  <circle id="b-dot-1" class="graph-dot blue" cx="0" cy="0" r="5.5"></circle>
                  <circle id="b-dot-2" class="graph-dot blue" cx="0" cy="0" r="5.5"></circle>
                  <circle id="b-dot-3" class="graph-dot blue" cx="0" cy="0" r="5.5"></circle>
                </svg>
                <div class="graph-labels">
                  <span>今月</span>
                  <span>3ヶ月後</span>
                  <span>6ヶ月後</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <button class="primary-button" type="button" data-toast="出費管理の開始導線を想定しています。">出費管理をはじめる</button>
              <button class="secondary-button" type="button" data-toast="売り時通知の設定モーダルを想定しています。">売り時通知を受け取る</button>
            </section>

            <div class="memory-strip">
              <div class="memory-card">
                <div class="memory-icon">⛽</div>
                <div class="memory-text">
                  <strong id="b-memory-title">先月より出費が落ち着いています</strong>
                  <span id="b-memory-sub">給油頻度が下がり、月間コストが3,200円減少</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="memory-card">
                <div class="memory-icon">🔔</div>
                <div class="memory-text">
                  <strong id="b-memory-title-2">売り時のサインを見逃さない</strong>
                  <span id="b-memory-sub-2">査定価格が5万円以上動いたら通知する設定</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="screen-footer">
              Google Play 2枚目向け想定 / 出費管理と将来予測で継続価値を訴求
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="shot" data-shot="c">
        <div class="shot-head">
          <div>
            <div class="shot-tag compare">スクショC / 競合比較</div>
            <h2 class="shot-title">「電話0本」で、<br />比較の不安をいちばん先に消す。</h2>
            <p class="shot-desc">
              相場だけ知りたい人にとって、営業電話が来ないことは大きな価値です。
              ただし売却相談に進む段階では1社対応になるため、その切り替わりも正直に見せています。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="shot-note">
            <strong>狙い</strong><br />
            比較サービスに疲れている層へ、
            「まずは見るだけでいい」を最短で伝えます。
          </div>
        </div>

